entries.title: Andrew Tate said he broke a woman’s jaw and that his business was a ‘scam’ ahead of Romanian arrest
entries.description: Andrew Tate's arrest in Romania follows a years-long history of public statements from Tate and others about his business model and the role women played in it.

entries.title: Amazon discontinues charity donation program amid cost cuts
entries.description: Amazon said Wednesday it plans to shut down its charity donation program, in the latest example of the company’s broader cost-cutting efforts.
